@page "/projects"
@layout MainLayout

<PageTitle>Donna's Projects - Learning Journey 🌸</PageTitle>

<div class="text-center mb-4">
    <span class="header-flower">📚</span>
    <h1>My Little Projects</h1>
    <span class="header-flower">📚</span>
</div>

<p class="text-center">These are the things I've been working on while learning to code!<br>
<small>✨ They might be simple, but I'm proud of every single one ✨</small></p>

<div class="projects-list">
    
    <!-- Current Portfolio Website -->
    <div class="project-item card mb-4" id="portfolio">
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="project-emoji">🎀</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">This Portfolio Website!</h3>
            <p class="card-text">The website you're looking at right now! I built this using Blazor to showcase my journey as an IT student from Kinatarcan Island. It's my first real web project and I'm learning so much from it! 💖</p>
            <div class="project-details">
                <span class="project-tag">🌐 Web Development</span>
                <span class="project-tag">⚡ Blazor</span>
                <span class="project-tag">🎨 HTML/CSS</span>
            </div>
            <p class="project-note mt-2"><small>💭 Still improving this everyday!</small></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Simple Calculator -->
    <div class="project-item card mb-4" id="calculator">
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="project-emoji">🧮</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Simple Calculator</h3>
            <p class="card-text">A basic calculator website where you can add, subtract, multiply, and divide numbers. Nothing fancy, but it works! This helped me understand JavaScript and how to handle user inputs. 🎯</p>
            <div class="project-details">
                <span class="project-tag">🔢 JavaScript</span>
                <span class="project-tag">📱 Responsive</span>
                <span class="project-tag">✨ Beginner Friendly</span>
            </div>
            <p class="project-note mt-2"><small>💭 My first interactive website!</small></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Chatbox Website -->
    <div class="project-item card mb-4" id="chatbox">
        <div class="card-body">
            <div class="project-emoji">💬</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Simple Chatbox Website</h3>
            <p class="card-text">A basic chat interface where users can send and receive messages. I'm still working on this one! It's teaching me about real-time interactions and how chat applications work behind the scenes. 🗨️</p>
            <div class="project-details">
                <span class="project-tag">💬 Real-time</span>
                <span class="project-tag">🔄 Work in Progress</span>
                <span class="project-tag">🌟 Learning Project</span>
            </div>
            <p class="project-note mt-2"><small>💭 Still fixing bugs but getting there!</small></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="encouragement-box text-center">
    <p>🌸 <strong>I know these are just simple projects</strong> 🌸<br>
    But everyone starts somewhere, right?<br>
    I'm proud of every little thing I create because each one teaches me something new.<br>
    <strong>From Kinatarcan Island, learning one line of code at a time 💪💕</strong></p>
    
    <div class="progress-note mt-3">
        <span>⭐ Where I'm at: Beginner but determined ⭐</span>
    </div>
</div>

<!-- Optional: Add a "What I Want to Build Next" section -->
<div class="dream-projects mt-4">
    <h3 class="text-center">💭 Projects I Want to Try Next 💭</h3>
    <div class="dream-list">
        <span>📝 To-Do List App</span>
        <span>🌤️ Weather App</span>
        <span>📸 Photo Gallery</span>
        <span>🎵 Music Player</span>
    </div>
    <p class="text-center small mt-2"><em>Hopefully soon! 🤞</em></p>
</div>